      <p class='text-2xl font-bold text-red-500 mb-2' style='font-family: Impact, "Arial Black", sans-serif;'>
        CALL NOW: 1-800-WILL-IT-CLAW
      </p>
      <p class='text-gray-500 text-xs outfit'>
        *Not a real phone number. Do not actually call. If you did call and someone answered, that's between you and them.
      </p>
    </div>

    <hr class='border-gray-700 mb-4' />

    <div class='flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4'>
      <p class='outfit text-gray-400 text-sm'>
        Will it Claw?‚Ñ¢ is a production of <a
